channel.title: Portforwarding a linksys WRT54G2? Or any1 with a linksys router
channel.description: Lol, im sorry, im like retarded :/ (not literally, just in computers) Idk how to portforward a linksys router, everyone says their the easiest but lol... Okay i have everything good, but idk what the static IP is, ok well i sat at my computer for 1hr and then finally someone came into the computer chat room and they gave me my DNS's and i need help from there. I was using PF.com but i didnt get it, after i did it for vista i didnt know what the static ip was, it doesnt tell you :l If someone can tell me how to get your static ip that would be marvelous. (lol) Thankz :D
